1. Determine which pizza shop to order pizza from
2. Determine how to order the pizza (mobile or telephone)
3. Find pizza shop number
4. Call the pizza shop
5. Choose and order your pizza
6. Decide whether you really want the pizza
7. Pay for the pizza
8. If you are feeling lonely, Call and invite friends to eat pizza together to avoid fat-shaming yourself
8. Wait patiently, remembering that these people are on minimum wage and may have had a tough day.
9. If the pizza is taking a long time, track the pizza on the app
10. DO NOT call them a "filthy animal"
11. Tip the delivery driver
12. Eat the pizza